eatures can live out a normal life. Well...as normal as it can be. \nWritten & Performed by Ariel Greenspoon \nThis show runs every Friday @ 9pm in February, if we can keep the monsters under control long enough. \n$5 online/$7 @ door BYOB", "html"=>"<P STYLE=\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif; line-height: 19px;\">In the 1960's, the tiny town of Point Pleasant, West Virginia, was rocked by a sudden appearance of the legendary Mothman. Many of the Mothman tales were locked away or excessively changed by those wanting a cheap thrill on Halloween. Now, the only official biographer of urban legends, Dr. Nelson Stern, is finally unveiling his wide collection of interviews, clips, &amp; videos so the world can fully understand the Mothman. Proving that even disgusting, horrid, dusty yet somehow slimy creatures can live out a normal life. Well...as normal as it can be.</P>\r\n<P STYLE=\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif; line-height: 19px;\">Written &amp; Performed by Ariel Greenspoon</P>\r\n<P STYLE=\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif; line-height: 19px;\">This show runs every Friday @ 9pm in February, if we can keep the monsters under control long enough.</P>\r\n<P STYLE=\"color: #333333; font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', 'Bitstream Charter', Times, serif; line-height: 19px;\"><STRONG>$5 online/$7 @ door</STRONG><BR><STRONG>BYOB</STRONG> </P>"}, "logo"=>{"id"=>"12020239", "url"=>"http://cdn.evbuc.com/images/12020239/58397944/1/logo.png"}, "id"=>"15126181817", "url"=>"http://www.eventbrite.com/e/classified-im-a-monster-tickets-15126181817?aff=ebapi", "logo_url"=>"http://cdn.evbuc.com/images/12020239/58397944/1/logo.png", "start"=>{"timezone"=>"America/Chicago", "local"=>"2015-02-06T21:00:00", "utc"=>"2015-02-07T03:00:00Z"}, "end"=>{"timezone"=>"America/Chicago", "local"=>"2015-02-27T22:00:00", "